ny\n- Shell (`op.shell`): preview_available=false, requires_approval=false, runtime_executable=false, decision=deny\n- Python REPL (`op.python_repl`): preview_available=false, requires_approval=false, runtime_executable=false, decision=deny\n- Memory write candidate (`op.memory_write_candidate`): preview_available=false, requires_approval=false, runtime_executable=false, decision=deny\nUse only the visible allow / approval / denied state; do not infer hidden permission changes.\nProjection must not grant permissions; authorization_owner=ResourcePolicy.\n\n### 投影姿态\nProjection role: analyst. Posture tags: concise.\n\n### 输出边界\nOutput should satisfy task modes: request_intake. Return a concise preview-ready response.\n\n### 护栏\nDo not execute tools, workers, file writes, shell commands, or memory writes in preview.\nDo not treat ResourceRuntimeView.authorized as runtime_executable.\nReview policy: optional."}, {"role": "user", "content": "给我一个简短结论"}], "history_message_count": 0, "pending_user_message_chars": 8, "system_prompt_chars": 2335, "token_pressure": {"pressure_level": "normal", "token_accounting": {}, "compaction_strategy": "none"}, "prompt_source_report": {"assembly_mode": "runtime_prompt_assembly", "legacy_system_prompt_chars": 425, "runtime_system_prompt_chars": 2335, "projection_ref": "987276492cdfb078", "prompt_manifest_ref": "manifest-987276492cdfb078", "manifest_section_count": 6, "runtime_section_count": 6, "context_selected_sections": [], "context_pressure_level": "normal", "manifest_sections": [{"order": 0, "section_id": "task_section", "source_type": "task_contract", "source_id": "turn:session-runtime-directive:1", "owner_layer": "task", "cache_scope": "dynamic", "visible_to_model": true, "chars": 124}, {"order": 1, "section_id": "method_section", "source_type": "skill_runtime_view", "source_id": "task_prompt_contract.method_section", "owner_layer": "skill", "cache_scope": "dynamic", "visible_to_model": true, "chars": 44}, {"order": 2, "section_id":